nodes.text: A human woman served as the proprietor of a common house on Sorgan, in 9 ABY. She served Din Djarin and Grogu during their visit to the common house. Din Djarin asked her questions about another patron, Carasynthia Dune, but the proprietor was unable to answer his questions. She later observed a brawl between Dune and a Zabrak fighter, and later continued serving patrons once it had concluded.

The proprietor first appeared in Chapter 4 of Jon Favreau's 2019 Disney+ television series The Mandalorian, portrayed by Ida Darvish, which aired on November 29, 2019. She was identified in the closing credits only as "Common House Proprietor."
